OL,3,CCardiologist calls for investigation
OL,4,Cinto Covid-19 vaccine
OL,6,FA cardiologist is calling for an
OL,7,Finvestigation into the safety of the
OL,8,Fvaccine after reportedly seeing a rise
OL,9,Fin the number of people with heart
OL,10,Fissues.
OL,12,FDr Dean Patterson says he is not an
OL,13,Fanti-vaxxer but wants to open a debate
OL,14,Fabout possible side effects from the
OL,15,Fvaccine roll-out.
OL,17,FHe adds: "I am an experienced
OL,18,Fclinician and I would never stand up
OL,19,Fand say something as I have, I am
OL,20,Finherently quite shy, it takes a lot
OL,21,Fto get me moving. It takes a lot."
