OL,4,Cinto Covid-19 vaccine
OL,6,FDr Patterson says: "People think I
OL,7,Fmust have come to this conclusion just
OL,8,Flike that but I haven't. It's been
OL,9,Frunning on guts, instinct at first,
OL,10,Fnot being quite happy, trying to speak
OL,11,Fto people then hoping to prove myself
OL,12,Fwrong.
OL,14,F"I think the scientific debate has
OL,15,Fbeen stifled. People and doctors have
OL,16,Fbeen threatened and lost their jobs,
OL,17,FI've had nursing staff at the hospital
OL,18,Fcontact me and say they can't speak
OL,19,Fout because of disciplinaries.
