OL,4,Cinto Covid-19 vaccine
OL,6,F"It's well known that this process is
OL,7,Fembedded in the past few years. It's
OL,8,Fnever happened before and I believe
OL,9,Fthat's the reason I'm on my own."
OL,11,FHowever, Guernsey's Health and Social
OL,12,FCare department and the island's
OL,13,FMedical Specialist Group say the
OL,14,Fbenefits of the vaccination far
OL,15,Foutweigh the side effects.
