OL,6,FDirector of Public Health, Dr Nicola
OL,7,FBrink, Medical Director Dr Peter Rabey
OL,8,Fand Chair of the Medical Specialist
OL,9,FGroup, Dr Steve Evans, explain: "Dr
OL,10,FPatterson's views on the Covid
OL,11,Fvaccines are not shared by the
OL,12,Fmajority of doctors and scientists in
OL,13,FGuernsey and across the world.
OL,15,F"There is clear and overwhelming
OL,16,Fsupport for the safety and
OL,17,Feffectiveness of Covid-19 vaccines,
OL,18,Fbased on evidence from a huge amount
OL,19,Fof ongoing research.
